Patch Set 1:

Hmmm, just for my information - why migrations tests don't run on DB2?

Patch Set 1:

Victor, oslo.db doesn't yet have support for running migrations with DB2, and the DB2 migrations should be run via the DB2 third party CI - which is what I'm assuming this patch is supposed to fix.

Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1

(2 comments)

You should have comments in the code for where DB2 needs to be different and why.

Also, you'll have to skip test_models_sync since it's not going to work with DB2 since the models have to be different:

http://logs.openstack.org/01/167101/1/check/gate-glance-python27/dc5f1ef/console.html#_2015-03-24_05_51_12_973
